                                <h4>Information about cookies</h4>
                                <p>As part of offering and providing customizable and personalized services, OVAL uses cookies to store and sometimes track information about you. A cookie is a small amount of data that is sent to your browser from a web server and stored on your computer’s hard drive. All sites on OVAL where you are prompted to login or that are customizable require that you accept cookies.</p>
                                <p>Generally, we use cookies to:</p>
